</emphasis>
two parallel rows of compressed supratympanic scales in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1845" box="[901,1002,1514,1537]" class="Reptilia" family="Agamidae" genus="Calotes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Squamata" pageId="24" pageNumber="425" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="maria">
